data.description: Charming 1 story 3 bedroom, 2 bath home nestled on a cul-de-sac in small community of Nopalitos. This model like home welcomes you with an open floor plan, natural light throughout, vinyl flooring in major living areas, 2 spacious bedrooms which one is currently being used as an office, laundry room and guest bath. Living room is open and overlooks dining area, lovely white kitchen with granite countertops, GE Energy Star stainless steel appliances, microwave, gas cooking and breakfast bar! Primary features brand new plush carpet, full bath and large closet! Enjoy relaxing fall evenings on your premium sized lot, oversized extended patio and chimenea seating area perfect for roasting marshmallows! This community features a super convenient location with easy access to FM 78, Walzem Rd., IH 35, Loop 410 and Brooke Army Medical Center. Come and see this like new move in ready home today!
